parameters.name: TYPE
parameters.description:
Telescope ID with which the event            
                                 is associated.  Range of value: 20 - 28

parameters.name: E1
parameters.description: Energy (MeV) deposited in the e1 detector

parameters.name: E2
parameters.description: Energy (MeV) deposited in the e2 detector

parameters.name: E3
parameters.description: Energy (MeV) deposited in the e3 detector

parameters.name: DZ
parameters.description:
Difference of 2 calculations of nuclear      
                                 charge; indicates approximate error in <Z>.

parameters.name: EAVG
parameters.description:
Rough estimate of incident energy of         
                                 particle.

parameters.name: SCTHAVG
parameters.description:
Rough estimate of secant of                  
                                 incident angle of particle

parameters.name: LIVETIME
parameters.description:
livetime (in seconds) appropriate for        
                                 the event; calculated from the ratio of      
                                 rates to telemetered events.

parameters.name: GF
parameters.description:
Geometry factor appropriate for the event    
                                 type.
